OL,3,CTories pledge to make 'biological sex'
OL,4,Cprotected characteristic
OL,6,FThe have pledged to change the
OL,7,FEquality Act to define the protected
OL,8,Fcharacteristic of sex as "biological
OL,9,Fsex".
OL,11,FThey claim the change will make it
OL,12,Fsimpler for service providers for
OL,13,Fwomen and girls, such as those running
OL,14,Fsessions for domestic abuse victims,
OL,15,Fto prevent biological males from
OL,16,Ftaking part.
