OL,3,CTories pledge to make 'biological sex'
OL,4,Cprotected characteristic
OL,6,FThe sex of those with a Gender
OL,7,FRecognition Certificate will still
OL,8,Falign with their acquired gender in
OL,9,Flaw outside the Equality Act, for
OL,10,Fexample marriage law, as is the status
OL,11,Fquo.
OL,13,FUnder the new scheme the Conservatives
OL,14,Fwill also establish in law that gender
OL,15,Frecognition is a reserved matter, as
OL,16,Fthey say "this will mean that an
OL,17,Findividual can only have one sex in
OL,18,Fthe eyes of the law in the United
OL,19,FKingdom".
