OL,4,Cprotected characteristic
OL,6,FPrime Minister Rishi Sunak said: "The
OL,7,Fsafety of women and girls is too
OL,8,Fimportant to allow the current
OL,9,Fconfusion around definitions of sex
OL,10,Fand gender to persist.
OL,12,F"The Conservatives believe that making
OL,13,Fthis change in law will enhance
OL,14,Fprotections in a way that respects the
OL,15,Fprivacy and dignity of everyone in
OL,16,Fsociety.
OL,18,F"We are taking an evidence-led
OL,19,Fapproach to this issue so we can
OL,20,Fcontinue to build a secure future for
OL,21,Feveryone across the whole country."
